high_descs: Take a step forward then turn left and walk across the room, hang a left and walk up to the left side of the red couch.
Pick up the red credit card off of the red couch.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the couch.
Put the red credit card in the cardboard box on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box with the credit card in it off of the couch.
Walk over to the round black table to the right of the television.
Put the cardboard box with the credit card in it on the round black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a credit card in it on a round black table.

high_descs: Turn left at the window, turn left at the rug,  and face the box on the red couch.
Pick up the credit card in front of the box.
Move over to the right a bit and face the box.
Put the credit card inside of the box.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn around and walk to the small table to the right of the television.
Place the box on the small table.
anns.task_desc: To put a credit card in a box and put the box on a small table.

high_descs: Turn left, go past the ottoman, turn left, go to the box on the couch.
Pick up the red credit card on the couch.
Bring the card to the box on the couch.
Put the card in the box on the couch.
Pick up the box with card on the couch.
Turn around, bring the box to the middle of the room by the ottoman, turn left, go to the small black round table.
Put the box on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with credit card on the small, round, black table.
